events.name: Hackathon @ University Malaya 2012
events.about:
Full day Hackathon from 9.00 am to 6.30 pm. 

9.00 am - Keynote by Google Student Ambassador representative

9.15 am - Keynote by University Malaysia Computer Science club, rules and guidelines of hackathon

9.30 am - Start hacking!

12.30 pm - Pizzas time ^^

6.00 pm - Pitch your app!

6.15 pm - Announcement of winning teams

6.30 pm - End
events.address: 3, IPS Building University of Malaya, Universiti Malaya
